    "body" : "<p>I strongly suggest using the <a href=\"http://java.sun.com/javase/6/docs/jre/api/javaws/jnlp/javax/jnlp/PersistenceService.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><code>PersistenceService</code></a>, part of <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Java_Web_Start#Java_Network_Launching_Protocol_(JNLP)\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><em>Java Network Launching Protocol (JNLP)</em></a>.</p>\n"
